{"tid":2353414,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好似我咁18歲就禿頭","createTime":"2021-01-04T17:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T13:59:59.000Z","uid":368368,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"b854184770a8036e45c7f13beaa0c89dee78fb6e","tid":2353414,"uid":368368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:11:32.000Z","msg":"其實我細細個大約10歲左右就瘋狂甩頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲同學見到笑我脫髮 跟著我返屋企同阿媽講呢件事<br />\n<br />\n阿媽就話<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">唔洗擔心，你換頭髮姐，好快就生番出嚟</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但結果係......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一直都冇撚生過啊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n期間有睇過中醫 西醫 連生髮專門店都去過<br />\n<br />\n但係咩用都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中醫話我夜訓 但係當時我十點半就上床訓覺<br />\n<br />\n西醫話我油脂分泌旺盛 但係而家食咗抗油脂藥都係瘋狂甩頭髮<br />\n<br />\n生髮專門店幫我洗頭 照燈 注氧 咩都試過 但係唔見成效<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">救命！！！有冇巴打知點做好</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c802de66b38ec28016708fe6360b9b14161334","tid":2353414,"uid":30468,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:16:00.000Z","msg":"剃光頭帶假髮"},{"pid":"08bfc8ff0805e5a58a9fb5aa81331b8b7e90342f","tid":2353414,"uid":208940,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"光頭幾好吖，慳返飛髪，洗頭水錢，只不過有樣野唔好，就係&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">呢世都溝唔到女，除非發達</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c486d1d3d6af8cd1391f5ef9f661d8fe2433eda","tid":2353414,"uid":199592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"額頭幾cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1997fc64c0e80e2f52c029b140480445ef8183d9","tid":2353414,"uid":301989,"like":5,"disl